title: Ep. 163 - Male Miss Universe Contestant Appropriates Womanhood
description:
Today on the show: more information has come out in the case of the 7 year old girl who died in the care of Border Patrol. It’s becoming clearer and clearer that Border Patrol did nothing wrong, but that’s not what the Left is saying. Also, a man competed in the Miss Universe pageant. How is that not "appropriation"? Date: 12-17-2018
